io.netty.util.concurrent

Interface Future

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChannelFuture, ChannelFuture.Unsafe, ChannelGroupFuture, ChannelPromise, Promise
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompleteFuture, CompletePromise, DefaultChannelPromise, DefaultPromise, FailedFuture, SucceededFuture

    public interface Future
    The result of an asynchronous operation.

    • Method Detail

      • isDone

        boolean isDone()
        Returns true if and only if this future is complete, regardless of whether the operation was successful or failed.

      • isSuccess

        boolean isSuccess()
        Returns true if and only if the I/O operation was completed successfully.

      • cause

        Throwable cause()
        Returns the cause of the failed I/O operation if the I/O operation has failed.
        Returns:
        the cause of the failure. null if succeeded or this future is not completed yet.

      • addListener

        Future addListener(GenericFutureListener<? extends Future> listener)
        Adds the specified listener to this future. The specified listener is notified when this future is done. If this future is already completed, the specified listener is notified immediately.

      • addListeners

        Future addListeners(GenericFutureListener<? extends Future>... listeners)
        Adds the specified listeners to this future. The specified listeners are notified when this future is done. If this future is already completed, the specified listeners are notified immediately.

      • removeListener

        Future removeListener(GenericFutureListener<? extends Future> listener)
        Removes the specified listener from this future. The specified listener is no longer notified when this future is done. If the specified listener is not associated with this future, this method does nothing and returns silently.

      • removeListeners

        Future removeListeners(GenericFutureListener<? extends Future>... listeners)
        Removes the specified listeners from this future. The specified listeners are no longer notified when this future is done. If the specified listeners are not associated with this future, this method does nothing and returns silently.

      • sync

        Future sync()
            throws InterruptedException
        Waits for this future until it is done, and rethrows the cause of the failure if this future failed.
        Throws:
        InterruptedException

      • syncUninterruptibly

        Future syncUninterruptibly()
        Waits for this future until it is done, and rethrows the cause of the failure if this future failed.

      • await

        Future await()
             throws InterruptedException
        Waits for this future to be completed.
        Throws:
        InterruptedException - if the current thread was interrupted

      • awaitUninterruptibly

        Future awaitUninterruptibly()
        Waits for this future to be completed without interruption. This method catches an InterruptedException and discards it silently.

      • await

        boolean await(long timeout,
            TimeUnit unit)
              throws InterruptedException
        Waits for this future to be completed within the specified time limit.
        Returns:
        true if and only if the future was completed within the specified time limit
        Throws:
        InterruptedException - if the current thread was interrupted

      • await

        Throws:
        InterruptedException - if the current thread was interrupted

      • awaitUninterruptibly

        boolean awaitUninterruptibly(long timeout,
                           TimeUnit unit)
        Waits for this future to be completed within the specified time limit without interruption. This method catches an InterruptedException and discards it silently.
        Returns:
        true if and only if the future was completed within the specified time limit
